                <h1>How to Fix Peel and Stick Wallpaper That Keeps Falling Off</h1>
                <p>Peel and stick wallpaper can be a stylish, easy home decor solution, but sometimes it falls off, leaving your walls bare. Common reasons for this issue include improper surface preparation, high humidity, or using low-quality materials. To fix it, make sure your walls are clean and smooth, and choose a reliable brand for a long-lasting bond.</p>
